been invited to Kitchen X.

31:48.400 --> 31:50.259
That's great, hun.

31:50.260 --> 31:53.799
I wish I wasn't outta
town or I'd go with you.

31:53.800 --> 31:56.169
Although, you might
wanna be careful

31:56.170 --> 31:58.289
who you share this info with.

31:58.290 --> 32:01.989
You haven't told
anyone else, have you?

32:01.990 --> 32:04.429
No, no, I promised
Chef John I wouldn't,

32:04.430 --> 32:05.780
but I had to tell somebody.

32:06.887 --> 32:09.073
Hannah, this is it.

32:10.800 --> 32:12.765
This is what my life has
been heading towards.

32:12.766 --> 32:14.189
