your car here.

34:47.610 --> 34:49.159
What the hell is that?

34:49.159 --> 34:50.418
Bottle of wine I
brought for dinner.

34:50.420 --> 34:52.509
No, don't even think
about bringing that.

34:52.510 --> 34:55.199
Greg and Beth are
pairing wines tonight.

