Greg and Beth from
the Wine Dungeon?

34:57.080 --> 34:58.040
The very same.

34:58.041 --> 35:00.573
Do yourself a favor,
leave that in your car.

35:19.560 --> 35:21.449
How many of these things
have you been to, Chef?

35:21.450 --> 35:22.819
Quite a few now.

35:22.820 --> 35:24.379
